{"tid":1799950,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU 認證！張滿月社長即將和《德魯納酒店》團隊 MT 出遊～","createTime":"2019-12-27T10:46:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T14:33:16.000Z","uid":16659,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4ce2379cfeb6074721323f9294313729ae11ce93","tid":1799950,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T10:46:58.000Z","msg":"感情也太好了吧～！期待那幾天更新的動態消息。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n熱門韓劇《德魯納酒店》已劇終將近四個月，整個團隊依舊有在聯繫，甚至在近期會一起出遊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nIU 在抵達巡迴演唱會的最後一站雅加達時，透過了 Instagram Stories 回答了粉絲們的提問。在被問到「現在和德魯納團隊是否還會經常見面呢？」她回答道：「馬上就要進行MT了。」本人直接預告了即將相聚的消息，讓劇迷們也相當期待。<br />\n<br />\n* MT 意思是&quot;Member training&quot;，類似社團的旅行或者研討活動，一般大學生辦活動時常用的詞<br />\n<br />\n▼12月15日 tvN 的年末快樂展上，主要演員齊聚合照，IU 更新 po 文：「沒有忘記德魯納的各位請雙手在頭頂比滿月。」"},{"pid":"3d12a19d16b2004efcf15f482d6b8aa52e44697d","tid":1799950,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T10:47:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/ef614947ab22991724676064dc3947d9/tumblr_py8usczdj81r7qnpao10_400.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2Fef614947ab22991724676064dc3947d9%2Ftumblr_py8usczdj81r7qnpao10_400.gifv&h=4cc945ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/d73fea9e0ce561c9690e9a7b03f04795/tumblr_py8usczdj81r7qnpao7_400.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2Fd73fea9e0ce561c9690e9a7b03f04795%2Ftumblr_py8usczdj81r7qnpao7_400.gifv&h=13bd098a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/d48f109d2735dffa6727f7e3d0b0686d/tumblr_py8usczdj81r7qnpao2_400.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2Fd48f109d2735dffa6727f7e3d0b0686d%2Ftumblr_py8usczdj81r7qnpao2_400.gifv&h=621e7cf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n社長愉快多p"},{"pid":"ba73f64e5e5e0b82e408631816a9e854f80a7114","tid":1799950,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T10:4